Chunkz won the first edition in 2024.  Aboflah took his revenge in 2025.

All the funds go to support quality education for disadvantaged young people across the Middle East, Asia and Africa

beIN SPORTS.desc: انغمس في إثارة كرة اليد الفرنسية مع Liqui Moly Starligue، القسم الأول من LNH سابقًا. تأسس هذا الحدث في الدوري الممتاز عام 1952، ويضم 16 فريقًا من أفضل الفرق يتقاتلون من أجل المجد.
beIN SPORTS.title_fr: Tremblay vs Paris - LNH Division 1 - Starligue Française de Handball
beIN SPORTS.desc_en: Dive into the excitement of French handball with Liqui Moly Starligue, formerly LNH Division 1. Champions earn spots in the EHF Champions League, while cup winners qualify for the European League.

beIN SPORTS XTRA 9.title: اليوم 1 - الجولة الأولى - بطولة ATP 500 ابن عمرو المفتوحة - روتردام 2026
beIN SPORTS XTRA 9.desc: واحدة من أطول البطولات الداخلية في جولة ATP، يتم التنافس على بطولة ABN AMRO المفتوحة على الملاعب الصلبة الداخلية السريعة في روتردام أهوي.
beIN SPORTS XTRA 9.title_fr: Jour 1 - M1 - ATP 500 Abn Amro Open - Rotterdam 2026
beIN SPORTS XTRA 9.desc_en: One of the longest-running indoor tournaments on the ATP Tour, the ABN AMRO Open is contested on fast indoor hard courts at Rotterdam Ahoy. The 32-player singles field competes for 500 ATP points and a total prize fund of €2,401,550, rewarding aggressive, first-strike tennis.
beIN SPORTS XTRA 9.desc_fr: L'un des tournois en salle les plus anciens du circuit ATP, l'ABN AMRO Open se dispute sur des courts intérieurs durs rapides à Rotterdam Ahoy.

beIN SPORTS 2.title_fr: Burnley vs West Ham United - Premier League anglaise 2025/2026 25ème journée
beIN SPORTS 2.desc_en: Burnley are winless in their last seven Premier League games against West Ham, having won four of their previous five against them. West Ham have won 53% of their Premier League games against Burnley. Among sides they’ve faced 10+ times in the competition, only against Watford  and Fulham  do they have a higher win rate.
